    "8) Challenges of developing LMMs.",
    "The development of LMMs faces challenges due to semantic gaps between different modalities,variations in noise levels between different modalities, and information loss when fusing multi-modal information.",
    "Differences in modality correlations across tasks or domains hinder direct model transferability.",
    "Furthermore, current multi-modal frameworks exhibit limitations."
